  "title": "Parry Shields",
  "description": "Adds new shield mechanics focused on parrying.",
  "body": "# 🛡️ Parry Shield Mod 🔰\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/parry-shields\">\n    <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/cu9F1Jua?style=for-the-badge&label=Modrinth\" alt=\"Modrinth Downloads\">\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/parry-shields\">\n    <img alt=\"CurseForge Downloads\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/1311336?style=for-the-badge&label=CurseForge\">\n  </a>\n</p>\n\n\n<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Shield Plus</th>\n      <th>Spike Shield</th>\n      <th>Slime Shield</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td align=\"center\">\n        <a href=\"#shield-plus\">\n          <img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1BuG4H77pOefuvEk3z88pUGRnYjLBvAhV&export=view&authuser=0\" alt=\"Shield Plus\" width=\"100%\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\">\n        <a href=\"#spike-shield\">\n          <img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1sfJq-0C34cM73sisDV1P2nqMnlNACRBg&export=view&authuser=0\" alt=\"Spike Shield\" width=\"100%\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td align=\"center\">\n        <a href=\"#slime-shield\">\n          <img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1B_GJf_r6PrI0hXsiO2GvWxUZ0YtFSSpk&export=view&authuser=0\" alt=\"Slime Shield\" width=\"100%\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Absorbing Shield</th>\n      <th>Soon</th>\n      <th>Soon</th>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n      <td colspan=\"1\" align=\"center\">\n        <a href=\"#absorbing-shield\">\n          <img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1gCoTU_haf3HnS7bdUU0LXJx7Zc1ANZ5o&export=view&authuser=0\" alt=\"Absorbing Shield\" width=\"100%\">\n        </a>\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"shield-plus\"><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1BuG4H77pOefuvEk3z88pUGRnYjLBvAhV&export=view&authuser=0\" alt=\"Slime Shield\" width=\"30px\"> Shield Plus:</h2>\n<blockquote>\n  If you successfully parry a melee attack, the attacker receives a <b>Stun effect</b>.<br>\n  Your next hit on the stunned attacker becomes a critical strike.\n</blockquote>\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.google.com/uc?export=view&id=1iM1J6_e-Z9YZYyyxqCz9at42pd1zYWYp\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"spike-shield\"><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1sfJq-0C34cM73sisDV1P2nqMnlNACRBg&export=view&authuser=0\" alt=\"Spike Shield\" width=\"30px\"> Spike Shield:</h2>\n<blockquote>\n  If you parry a melee attack, the attacker takes half the damage back.<br>\nJust holding the shield deals 1.5 hearts of damage to melee attackers.<br>\nWorks only against melee attacks.\n</blockquote>\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1DpwJCY8oh2dVXdlcnq6Rb6BSX1fg7r4I&export=view&authuser=0\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"slime-shield\"><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1B_GJf_r6PrI0hXsiO2GvWxUZ0YtFSSpk&export=view&authuser=0\" alt=\"Slime Shield\" width=\"30px\"> Slime Shield:</h2>\n<blockquote>\n  Parrying a melee hit knocks the attacker back <b>3 blocks</b>.<br>\n  Simply holding it knocks melee attackers back <b>1 block</b> on contact.<br>\n  Projectiles like arrows and tridents will bounce off this shield.\n</blockquote>\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=19GTgoQVDvx_CJD_4MUUg2PA1Gfm4c3zf&export=view&authuser=0\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1AgVcQwgP0ZsNoT4KdjgDzicX1m5XTLO7&export=view&authuser=0\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1Oq20A1qbGGNBs4Bq9FF2SI1odZGjrLO4&export=view&authuser=0\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n  </tr>\n</table>\n\n<h2 id=\"absorbing-shield\"><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1gCoTU_haf3HnS7bdUU0LXJx7Zc1ANZ5o&export=view&authuser=0\" alt=\"Absorbing Shield\" width=\"30px\"> Absorbing Shield:</h2>\n<blockquote>\n  If you successfully parry a melee attack, the attacker will drop their weapon and become stunned for a short time. <br>\nThis gives you an opportunity to counterattack while they are vulnerable.<br>\nWhen blocking projectiles (like arrows or tridents), they will either fall to the ground at your feet, or be added directly to your inventory. <br>\n</blockquote>\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1BTcObQcFGFZ5p1SnZCj48H9cstm-81Lp&export=view&authuser=0\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=10-w82OsOjb85BVo8fh3aS90Z2OMJB0aw&export=view&authuser=0\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1f3XCLriyLVqqCl1SLjuIp4WEu65KVQKG&export=view&authuser=0\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n    <td><img src=\"https://drive.usercontent.google.com/download?id=1efdaw3288SVp03cJu_J8EGMVzHyNVBzQ&export=view&authuser=0\" width=\"100%\"></td>\n  </tr>\n</table>",
